The paper discusses the self-organization of neurons and ants, and proposes a method for pattern recognition using artificial ant colonies in digital image habitats. This suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of distributed computation (cs.LG) in the proposed method.
